<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <title>Trial Reminder</title>
  <link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-wvfXpqpZZVQGK6TAh5PVlGOfQNHSoD2xbE+QkPxCAFlNEevoEH3Sl0sibVcOQVnN" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/3.5.2/animate.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="brand"><span>Trial</span> Reminder</h1>
    <div class="wrapper animated bounceInLeft">
      <div class="company-info">
        <h3>Making free trials free again</h3>
        Enter the name of the company and a link to the website, which will both be included in the message sent. Making it easier to access and cancel straight away.
        <br>
    
        <p> Please enter your email and phone number, this is how we will be able to contact you.
        <br>
         <br>
        Enter in a time which you want to receive the message.
         <br>
        <br>
        Enter a Date which is suitable like the day before due date for example
        <br>
         <br>
        Also a customer message maybe something to promt you like the cost if you don't cancel for example
        </p>
        
      </div>
      <div class="contact">
        <h3>Enter in the details below</h3>
        {{msg}}
        <form method="POST" action="send">
        
          <p>
            <label>Company Name</label>
            <input type="text" name="name">
          </p>
          <p>
            <label>Website</label>
            <input type="url" name="company">
          </p>
          <p>
            <label>Email Address</label>
            <input type="email" name="email">
          </p>
          <p>
            <label>Phone Number</label>
            <input type="text" name="phone">
          </p>
          <p>
            <label>Enter a time you want to receive the email</label>
            <input type="time" name="time">
          </p>
           <p>
            <label>Select a date for the email to be sent</label>
            <input type="date" name="picker">
          </p>
          <p class="full">
            <label>Message</label>
            <textarea name="message" rows="5"></textarea>
          </p>
          <p class="full">
            <button type="submit ">Submit</button>
          </p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>